                          "language": "en-US",
                          "approach": "procedural",
                          "explanation": "Let's count together! I have some blocks here. Watch what I do.\n\n*places one block*\nOne. Just one block, all by itself.\n\n*places another block*\nOne... two. Now we have two blocks.\n\n*places another*\nOne... two... three. Three blocks!\n\n*places another*\nOne... two... three... four.\n\n*places the last one*\nOne... two... three... four... five!\n\nFive blocks! Every time we add a block, we say the next number."
